rows.label: tlk00040101_msg0001
rows.name:
What you waiting for? Chop, chop!
You go see Chairman Bahn now!

rows.label: tlk00040101_msg0002
rows.name: What should I ask Punin about?

rows.label: tlk00040101_msg0005
rows.name:
Go through Avaritia Bazaar and up
stairs. Chairman's room right there.

rows.label: tlk00040101_msg0006
rows.name:
Meh! Stop this dilly-dally and hop to it!
You young and sprightly bod, no?

rows.label: tlk00040101_msg0007
rows.name:
Not bad, not bad. Wife ran out on me,
but apart from that, cannot complain.

rows.label: tlk00040101_msg0008
rows.name:
Punin's hands full with menial
tasks...I mean, very important work for
Chairman Bahn!

rows.label: tlk00040101_msg0009
rows.name:
High-powered role naturally leaves
Punin time-poor. But still important
to have breaky-break sometimes.

rows.label: tlk00040101_msg0010
rows.name:
Still, Punin incredibly jealous.
That reward 100 times of Punin's
monthly salary.

rows.label: tlk00040101_msg0011
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]If things go well, I should treat Punin
to a big plate of Samod...
